OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cbody found at Bronze Age stone circle
OL,6,FA murder investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched after a body was discovered
OL,8,Fat a Bronze Age stone circle in the
OL,9,FPeak District.
OL,11,FOfficers were called to Nine Ladies
OL,12,FStone Circle, in Stanton Lees at
OL,13,F1.38pm on Monday 22 June after reports
OL,14,Fof a man's body being found.
OL,16,FA 26-year-old was confirmed dead at
OL,17,Fthe scene.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
