OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1782402488
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cbody found at Bronze Age stone circle
OL,6,FPolice have said formal identification
OL,7,Fis yet to take place but that his
OL,8,Ffamily are aware and are being
OL,9,Fsupported by specialist officers.
OL,11,FAn investigation into the
OL,12,Fcircumstances of his death has been
OL,13,Flaunched.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
