OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1782402488
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cbody found at Bronze Age stone circle
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Tony Owen, from
OL,7,Fthe East Midlands Special Operations
OL,8,FUnit (EMSOU), who is leading the
OL,9,Finvestigation, said: "We know that
OL,10,Fthere have been a lot of people in the
OL,11,Farea of Nine Ladies Stone Circle over
OL,12,Fthe weekend celebrating the summer
OL,13,Fsolstice and this incident will
OL,14,Fundoubtedly be shocking and
OL,15,Fdistressing to those who were present,
OL,16,Fas well as the wider community.
OL,26,@qD@VOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
