PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1782402488
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cbody found at Bronze Age stone circle
OL,6,F"We know that this will be of concern
OL,7,Fto people and there will be an
OL,8,Fincreased police presence in the area
OL,9,Fover the coming days so I'd urge
OL,10,Fanyone with any concerns to please
OL,11,Fspeak to an officer."
OL,13,FA Major Incident Public Portal (MIPP)
OL,14,Fhas been set up where members of the
OL,15,Fpublic can send police information
OL,16,Fdirectly via this link ` Public Portal.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@UO]
